title: Need a little help
body:
Hey guys, I'm writing LoL stories because I'm bored.

They are couple stories, inspired by Zed x Syndra.

I've done Yasuo x Riven and part 1 of Fiora x Jax. I'm currently working on Pantheon x Morgana (bakers)

Id love it if you guys had some ideas to give me.

Thanks,
Seacaber

I wanted ideas, not hate.
